<h1 class="title">Andrew Buckingham's ITS Workshops</h1>
<div id="outline-container-sec-1" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-1">Presentation</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">
</div><div id="outline-container-sec-1-1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-1-1">Self-Introduction</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-1">
<p>
Andrew Buckingham <br  />
Software Support Analyst <br  />
UMKC Instructional Technologies <br  />
